snippet.title: Stealth Inc 2: A Game of Clones - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Stealth Inc 2: A Game of Clones is now available on Xbox One and will arrive on PC, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, and PlayStation Vita on April 7th.

Visit all of our channels:
Features & Reviews - http://www.youtube.com/user/gamespot
